{"tid":2037675,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"住院7個多月「賭王」何鴻燊今天出院","createTime":"2020-05-27T06:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:47:31.000Z","uid":202340,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9aeb8e4afe31030b1357c7a7d7bc8d0e56652a","tid":2037675,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:27:02.000Z","msg":"【大紀元3月6日報導】在養和醫院住院7個多月的澳博主席何鴻燊今日出院，他坐在輪椅上，由家人陪同離開，並向在場等候的記者揮手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天下午4時許，坐在輪椅上的何鴻燊在家人及醫師陪護下，離開位於跑馬地的養和醫院返家。<br />\n<br />\n何鴻燊的女兒何超瓊表示，父親的體重已回復至入院前的水平，亦可以自由走動。何超瓊說，有兩名主診醫生，陪同父親回家，家中已安裝醫療設備，又會測試設備是否足夠，預料何鴻燊會長時間留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n去年7月底，何鴻燊疑因跌傷，被送入香港的港安醫院治療。約2個月後轉入養和醫院。去年11月底，他在醫院中度過88歲生日。<br />\n<br />\n現場有約60名記者採訪，院方在門外劃出採訪區。 @"},{"pid":"201c20b6332428cb17a96b5be45feb4b9f26d470","tid":2037675,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700e424cc16e47801b388323227bbf8890737e24","tid":2037675,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5383dd46f2ff8d2b1d80a09a0cf317734c739462","tid":2037675,"uid":34935,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"琴日都算係出院既"},{"pid":"f7162dd7707731461cb2d508a18f4978a7f14887","tid":2037675,"uid":186177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5383dd46f2ff8d2b1d80a09a0cf317734c739462","tid":2037675,"uid":34935,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"琴日都算係出院既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"係'院出'囉唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee180fd4a96da2e186cb7496f6577afd00d62299","tid":2037675,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"賭王復活了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shock